	* infinoted/infinoted-signal.h:
	* infinoted/infinoted-signal.c: Implemented serial signal handling
	via libdaemon, handle SIGQUIT and SIGHUP signals. Bug #507 (Yarek
	"Fx3" Tyshchenko).

